<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.1">
<l>unti mēlnāṉ mukaṉaip paṭaittāṉulakuṇṭavaṉ</l>
<l>entai pemmā ṉimaiyōr kaḷtātaik  kiṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>canti ṉōṭu maṇiyuṅ koḻikkum puṉalkāviri</l>
<l>yanti pōlum niṟattār vayalcūḻ teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place of the father of the celestials,</l>
<l rend="indent">the great lord, our father</l>
<l>The one who ate the world, who created four-faced [Brahmā] on his navel,</l>
<l>Is Araṅkam of the South encircled by full paddy fields tinged like the sunset</l>
<l>[And by] the Kāviri whose waters cast up jewels along with sandalwood.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
